commits.content:
export function SearchIconRound({ className }: { className?: string }) {
  return (
    <svg
      width="34"
      height="34"
      viewBox="0 0 34 34"
      fill="none"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    >
      <circle
        cx="17"
        cy="17"
        r="16"
        stroke="white"
        strokeOpacity="0.4"
        strokeWidth="2"
      />
      <rect x="5" y="5" width="23" height="23" fill="white" />
    </svg>
  );
}
